{"tid":1145321,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"1萬上100萬，真飛派錢","createTime":"2019-05-08T15:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T12:14:17.000Z","uid":225187,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"6dd894c6a6cbf3264480d0c909f2381b45a7b1cc","tid":1145321,"uid":225187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5LOSi1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5LOSi1.jpg&h=c0e77140&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n哥倫布機員 (主) 對 洛杉磯銀河 (客)<br />\n首先倍率已經好唔正常<br />\n主隊近8場輸足6場，仲要連輸5場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但客隊近8場嬴足6場和一輸一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明顯客隊個態同勢都高幾班  居高排第二<br />\n但倍率得淡笑<br />\n竟然係主1.7  客3.7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔合常態<br />\n仲要客隊有E巴 同場場數人幾粒<br />\n真係唔明點解咁高水<br />\n但唔緊要  基於有假波理由 所以不合適買主客<br />\n所以<br />\n買攻力強勁既第一隊入球 客隊 先收左錢 之後打成點已經唔關我地事<br />\n第一注即刻ALL IN 谷大本金啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8e765ab0f93cd0c0b99522362b6c12e2f0aa1e","tid":1145321,"uid":141576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T15:34:36.000Z","msg":"跟"},{"pid":"b9a0b731b231afd0dae14470076b2c4b6b41954c","tid":1145321,"uid":12784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T15:36:22.000Z","msg":"跟"},{"pid":"38978e30a46c96335d520e4e2a42030ebb1508dc","tid":1145321,"uid":58867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T15:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />祝你好運"},{"pid":"053bae8c7de466ea0a4a2c7a01f35ff19d558d40","tid":1145321,"uid":93872,"li